This JQL:

{{created >= 2015-01-01 AND created <= 2015-01-31}}

returns *2465 *issues on jira.atlassian.com



The result of this two following queries should be equivalent to it:

{{created >= 2015-01-01 AND created <= 2015-01-15}}
{{created >= 2015-01-16 AND created <= 2015-01-31}}

but this delivers 1022 and 1352 results = *2374*!

So it seems that {{created <=}} actually does {{created <}}.

Our JIRA version is 6.3.5 also shows this error.
Please fix it

